= Game Mechanics =

This page documents the game mechanics of Yoshi's Cookie for the NES.

== Overview ==

Yoshi's Cookie is a puzzle game developed by Bullet-Proof Software (now Blue Planet Software) and published by Nintendo. Players must match rows and columns of cookies to clear them from the board.

