=== Yoshi Cookie Special ===

The Yoshi Cookie is a wild card that:
* Can complete any row or column
* Appears rarely
* Worth bonus points
* Clears entire row AND column when matched

== Game Modes ==

=== Action Mode ===

Standard puzzle mode:
* Cookies fall from top and right
* Clear cookies before board fills
* Speed increases with level
* Game over when board overflows

