== Technical Details ==

=== RNG Seed ===

Random number generator for cookie spawns:
* Initial seed from timer
* Linear congruential generator
* Period: 65536

=== Cookie Spawn Algorithm ===

New cookies spawn with weighted probability:

{| class="wikitable"
! Cookie !! Base Weight !! Notes
|-
| Heart || 20% || Equal weight
|-
| Diamond || 20% || Equal weight
|-
| Circle || 20% || Equal weight
|-
| Square || 20% || Equal weight
|-
| Flower || 18% || Slightly less
|-
| Yoshi || 2% || Rare
|}

Weights adjust based on board state to maintain fairness.

== Strategies ==

=== Basic Strategy ===

* Focus on one row/column at a time
* Set up chain reactions
* Save Yoshi Cookies for emergencies
* Watch incoming cookies

=== Advanced Techniques ===

* Stack matching cookies for chains
* Use column shifts to set up row clears
* Plan 2-3 moves ahead
* Keep board balanced

=== VS Mode Strategy ===

* Clear multiple rows/columns quickly
* Chains send more garbage
* Watch opponent's board
* Time clears to disrupt opponent

